name: King VS Mutant
description: When humans destroy the earth. Humans make pollution, cut down forests, build too many high buildings without thinking about the fate of the earth. what about water, forest, mountains, sea, air. All polluted. Industry also creates havoc with intentionally created viruses. Then nature is getting wrath. Natural disasters can't be avoided. Chicken vs mutant is just an analogy. For nature's revenge against humans who destroy nature
